HEADWORD: Pepsi-Cola
<hw>Pepsi-Cola</hw></mhw> <pos>prop. n.</pos>
<ety>[A trademark of the <org>Pepsi-Cola Corporation</org>.]</ety>
<def>A carbonated soft drink flavored by extract from the cola nut (kola
nut). The nut is found on trees of the species <spn>Cola acuminata</spn>
and <spn>Cola nitida</spn>.</def> <mark>[Trademark]</mark>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> Pepsi</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> + <source>PJC</source>]</p>


